; FrontPorch VoIP.ms dialplan hook.
;
; Copy this file to /etc/asterisk/extensions_voipms.conf on the deployed
; Asterisk host only if provider-specific dialplan glue is needed.
;
; Public DID handling is generated from Django PublicPhoneNumber records into
; conf.d/extensions_frontporch.conf under the frontporch-public-inbound context.
; The VoIP.ms PJSIP endpoint points there directly.
;
; This file is intentionally empty for the first trunk milestone. It does not
; route callers to children, provide voicemail, implement IVR behavior, enable
; outbound PSTN calling, or implement 911.
